Subject: List of flax diseases 
To: Kimberly
Content:
This article is a list of diseases of flax (Linum usitatissimum and other Linum spp.). Phoma spp. Phoma exigua var. linicola Aureobasidium lini Guignardia fulvida [teleomorph] Alternaria spp. Colletotrichum lini Fusarium spp. Pythium spp. Rhizoctonia solani Thanatephorus cucumeris [telomorph] Thielaviopsis basicola Chalara elegans [synanamorph] Septoria linicola Mycosphaerella linicola [teleomorph] Melampsora lini = Melampsora lini var. lini Extreme high or low temperatures cause cankers at soil level
I read the paragraph on http://wikipedia.org
